deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Tuesday, February 20. Order within 15 hrs 14 mins
features: Superior Sound Quality: Capture crystal-clear audio with PD200X USB dynamic microphone. The built-in dynamic mic capsule helps you to capture deep lows, delicate highs, and crisp mid-tones. Designed to deliver exceptional performance for podcasting, streaming, and recording

Advanced Software Control: Take your audio customization to the next level with MAONO Link software, allowing you to adjust various parameters and optimize your sound effortlessly. Set the perfect vocal tone, and you can turn on/off the RGB light or switch in 9 different colors, also supports EQ, limiter, and compressor adjustment in USB mode. (Software features are only available in USB mode)

Versatile Usage: The PD200X streaming microphone is equipped with USB and XLR dual interfaces. Plug-and-play when you are recording with a desktop or a laptop by plugging the 8.2ft USB cable directly. XLR analog output is for connecting to all professional interfaces, mixers, or portable PA systems when podcasting in your studio. Ideal for a wide range of applications, including podcasting, voiceovers, gaming, YouTube videos, music recording, and more

Easy Plug-and-Play Setup: Everything is in your control, simply connect the microphone to your computer via USB and start recording instantly. No additional drivers or complicated setups are required. The podcast microphone has a 2-in-1 smart knob to adjust the mic gain and headphone volume, the one-click mute key with LED indicator helps you to instantly mute the mic, and real-time monitoring of 3.5 mm headphone jack monitor output voice as desired by recording professionals

Adjustable and Flexible: MAONO PD200X podcast microphone kit features a sturdy and adjustable microphone boom arm, allowing you to position it at the perfect angle for optimal sound capture. Crafted with high-quality materials, higher standard microphone materials, and craftsmanship to protect the microphone's internal structure

Noise Reduction Technology: Ultra-wide frequency response of 40Hz-16KHz presents crystal clear and clean sound. Cardioid polar pattern reduces unwanted background noises in your recording and streaming

What's in The Box: Dynamic Microphone*1, Shock Mount*1, 2.5m USB-C to USB-A/C Cable*1, 5/8'' to 3/8'' Adapter*1, microphone boom arm*1, User's Manual*1, 18 Months Free Warranty (NOTE: XLR CABLE NOT INCLUDED)

Why are software and other additional functions only available in USB connection mode? USB and XLR connection methods have independent system and circuit designs. XLR mode transmits analog sound signals suitable for audio interface. USB mode converts analog signals to digital for additional functions like software control. What advantages does the MAONO PD200X XLR/USB Dynamic Microphone offer compared to other products? 1. PD200X comes with customized software that allows you to personalize mic parameters and EQ. 2. The mic incorporates cutting-edge technology and delivers professional audio output. 3. MAONO provides lifetime product firmware and software upgrades. How can I upgrade the firmware to access the latest features? Simply use MAONO Link software to check if your product is running the latest version. If not, visit the MAONO official website to download and install the newest firmware.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Love the all white color Mic and arm set, it matches to my desk setup :)
reviews.reviewText: Love the all white color Mic and arm set, it matches to my desk setup :)I'm so satisfied with the product!The main reason I order this is to match with my desk setup, Other than the Display and the laptop, most of my accessories is white color, so I was looking white mic arm.I didn't expect much for the sound quality of the mic, since it only cost less than $85 as a set.But, it surprised me with the sound quality of this mic.Of course compare to high end mic, there is a sound quality difference, but to be honest, not that much of the difference, which I may keep this set and mic for my home office (as a main mic) and take the better quality mic on black color to the work office desk.Good product, I'm happy with it :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super recomendado en relación calidad precio.
reviews.reviewText: Como amante de la tecnología he decidido probar este micrófono y me encontré con un diseño y construcción de excelente calidad, hecho de materiales metálicos, resistentes además de livianos, cuenta con un botón inteligente de dos funciones (control de ganancia y control de volumen) tanto para el micrófono como para supervisar nuestra voz en tiempo real, incluso mientras lo usamos incluso en la oscuridad, además, y si lo presionamos ligeramente nos activa la función de silenciar rápidamente el micrófono. Filtro Anti-pop de muy buen aspecto, agarre y función.Cuenta con una salida de cable USB tipo C para conectar fácilmente a una computadora de escritorio, portátil y/o celular. Además, cuenta con una salida analógica XLR para conectar a interfaces profesionales, mezcladoras o sistemas de PA portátiles.Los efectos RGB tienen efectos estáticos de colores sólidos, los cuales están muy bonitos y tienen un alto brillo configurables mediante un botón situado en la parte anterior del micrófono, la pega es que al ser un botón pequeño se hace algo incomodo de usar, recomiendo usar el software mientras se pueda.SI usamos el micrófono en modo USB se hace compatible con el software Maono-link que se descarga desde la página del fabricante, pudiendo encender/apagar la luz RGB o cambiar en cualquiera de los colores, también nos permite controlar la ganancia, el EQ, limitador y ajuste del compresor.El brazo extensor proporcionado en el paquete es de muy buena calidad y acabado (aluminio liviano y resistente), pudiéndose instalar casi de manera inmediata en cualquier lugar.Es una excelente elección tanto para tareas domésticas como para profesionales, siendo compatible con cualquier sistema a usar y proporcionando un sonido de excelente calidad.La única pega es que faltaron los velcros y algunas calcomanías del fabricante para hacerles publicidad, por lo demás, super recomendado en relación calidad precio.
